---
title: Middle Eastern Double Chicken & Veggie Couscous with Yoghurt Drizzle
description: Spice up your mealtime with this Middle Eastern-inspired delight! Juicy, honey-tossed chicken is paired with fluffy broccoli and carrot-studded couscous for a hearty base, while a cool, tangy yoghurt drizzle ties it all together. Fresh, flavourful and ready to transport your taste buds—this bowl is a total crowd-pleaser!
